itemDescription: Northern Irish politician, gardener, aviator, and philatelist

wikipedia_page.main: Lady Mary Elizabeth "Mairi" Bury (née Vane-Temptest-Stewart; 25 March 1921 - 16 November 2009), known between 1942 and 1958 as Viscountess Bury, was a Northern Irish politician, gardener, aviator, and philatelist.
